<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>

  <div class="faq-item open">
    <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="true" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      Can I switch plans at any time?
      <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <div class="faq-answer-inner">
        Absolutely. You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. When upgrading, you'll be prorated for the remainder of your billing cycle. When downgrading, the change takes effect at the start of your next billing period, and you'll retain access to the higher-tier features until then.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      What happens if I exceed my event limit?
      <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <div class="faq-answer-inner">
        We'll notify you when you reach 80% and 100% of your event quota. If you exceed your limit, your integrations will continue to run but new events will be queued. You can upgrade your plan to process them immediately, or they'll be processed in order at the start of the next billing cycle.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      Do you offer discounts for nonprofits or startups?
      <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <div class="faq-answer-inner">
        Yes! We offer 50% off Team plans for verified nonprofits and early-stage startups (under $1M in funding). Contact our sales team with your organization details, and we'll get you set up within 24 hours.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      Is there a free trial for Team or Scale plans?
      <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <div class="faq-answer-inner">
        Every paid plan comes with a 14-day free trial. No credit card required to start. You'll get full access to all features in the tier, and you can downgrade to the Starter plan at any time if it's not the right fit.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      How does the annual billing work?
      <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      <div class="faq-answer-inner">
        When you choose annual billing, you pay for 12 months upfront and receive a 20% discount compared to monthly billing. For the Team plan, that's $23/mo per user instead of $29/mo. Your payment is processed once per year, and you can switch back to monthly at the end of your billing term.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

